            <h3>Who</h3>
            <p>Developed by Larry Page and Sergey Brin, Google's PageRank algorithm revolutionized search engines during the Web 2.0 era.</p>

            <h3>What</h3>
            <p>PageRank ranks web pages based on the quality of inbound links, helping users find relevant content. Learn more about how PageRank works on the <a href="https://www.google.com/search/howsearchworks/algorithms/" target="_blank">Google Search Guide</a>.</p>

